title: The Creation V3
author: BKMDT123
pages:
#- Long Long Long (okay you get it) there was nothing but slime, rocks, and nether wart untill it got hit by a beam of light sent by the god of nature, Direction. The godess of knowlege, Sense gave it the abity to think for it's self. The god of progres,
#- Experience gave it the abity to learn. Direction made massive trees that he set on fire having the flames become the sun and light while the leaves became the clouds to hide the light and create darness but would bring a new light of light when someone
#- was brave enough to to make it go away. But do be warned he also added a self destrut button if one overused his creation he could take it away in an istant. Sense began inflicting beings with awarness so that they could harness Directions' creations. 
#- Experience planed out how he could help they're creations create there own things, aware that having the fight was nesary for peace as Direction had laid out.
